    - Required components: N, baseline, comparator, endpoint+timepoint
    - Template example with placeholders
    - Generalization: non-clinical domains mentioned
    - No drug-name hard-code in rule text
    - Non-regression: rules #10 (M-27) and #11 (M-29) still present
    - All rules 1-12 numbered
    
    tests_passed: 764/764 (+11 M-32)
    
    Expected V22 impact: per-trial claim frames should lift narrative
